{"tid":1492020,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"福布斯中國100名人榜公布　","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T17:38:01.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb855f9ee7d34f3b211e4cce679b1ba56d22550","tid":1492020,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:52:44.000Z","msg":"「福布斯中國100名人榜」今日出爐，由主演內地超人氣科幻電影《流浪地球》的演員吳京登榜首，其票房僅次於他自導自演的《戰狼2》，隨後有黃渤、胡歌，其餘十大入榜藝人以次序為徐崢、周杰倫、沈騰、周冬雨、組合TFBOYS成員易烊千璽、楊冪及吳亦凡。<br />\n<br />\n今次百大名人榜亦有香港藝人上榜，排最前的有陳偉霆（23位），再以次序有GOT7成員王嘉爾（40位）、古天樂（51位）、郭富城（56位）、成龍（69位）、張學友（74位）、鄧紫棋（77位）。<br />\n<br />\n至於憑2018年的內地宮延劇《延禧攻略》爆紅的吳謹言都順利入榜排第65位。最為港人熟悉的還有彭于晏（38位）、李榮浩（49位）、章子怡（54位）、李冰冰（76位）、舒淇（90位）、羅志祥（99位）。"},{"pid":"b72badf84078d4d8d7d317234a1c763e6ba1efb1","tid":1492020,"uid":2562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg&h=ba2d15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYuV4gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYuV4gf.jpg&h=52b2bc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tri4dee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftri4dee.png&h=7af3e96e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15aadb71f26d06a7175a